{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1d893038c0","title":"念奴娇·井冈山","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9ae4afd1f5","index":0,"year":1965,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"1d893038c0"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[{"id":"6c5d6db386","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"1d893038c0","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"五井碑，并冈山上有大井、小井、上井、中井、下井等地，总称五井。明清以来立有五井碑，现已段。"},{"id":"3739a193e2","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"1d893038c0","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"古代曾云海绿，有人说，这里古代曾经是海。"}],"contents":[{"id":"dbab3fce58","type":"title","text":"念奴娇·开冈山","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"1d893038c0"},{"id":"6c5d6db386","type":"paragraph","text":"参天万木，千百里，飞上南天奇岳。故地重来何所见，多了楼台亭阁。五井碑前，黄洋界上，车子飞如跃。江山如画，古代曾云海绿。以弹指三十八年，人间变了，似天渊翻覆。犹记当时烽火里，九死一生如昨。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"1d893038c0"},{"id":"3739a193e2","type":"subtitle","text":"独有豪情，","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"1d893038c0"},{"id":"5640de2bb8","type":"paragraph","text":"天际悬明月，风雷磅磷。一声鸡唱，万怪烟消云落。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"1d893038c0"}],"page":{"id":"22430f7fb5","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"1d893038c0","start":63,"end":64}}}},"__N_SSG":true}